<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/daisyui@2.33.0/dist/full.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.1.2/css/all.min.css" integrity="sha512-1sCRPdkRXhBV2PBLUdRb4tMg1w2YPf37qatUFeS7zlBy7jJI8Lf4VHwWfZZfpXtYSLy85pkm9GaYVYMfw5BC1A==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/favicon/favicon.ico">
    <title>Habla Good</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="navbar bg-base-100">
        <div class="navbar-start">
          <div class="dropdown">
            <label tabindex="0" class="btn btn-ghost lg:hidden">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 6h16M4 12h8m-8 6h16" /></svg>
            </label>
            <ul tabindex="0" class="menu menu-compact dropdown-content mt-3 p-2 shadow bg-base-100 rounded-box w-52">
              <li><a href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/socialchallengetls"><i class="fa-brands fa-tiktok"></i>#SocialChallengeTLS</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://discord.gg/3PnERvQZRe"><i class="fa-brands fa-discord"></i>Discord Community</a></li>
              <li><a href="#acerca-de"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-question"></i>Acerca De</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <a href="/" class="btn btn-ghost normal-case text-xl"><img src="/favicon/favicon.ico"></a>
        </div>
        <div class="navbar-center hidden lg:flex">
          <ul class="menu menu-horizontal p-0">
            <li><a href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/socialchallengetls"><i class="fa-brands fa-tiktok"></i>#SocialChallengeTLS</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://discord.gg/3PnERvQZRe"><i class="fa-brands fa-discord"></i>Discord Community</a></li>
            <li><a href="#acerca-de"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-question"></i>Acerca De</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="navbar-end">
          <a href="https://github.com/diathekez/live-messages-ejs" class="btn"><i class="fa-brands fa-github"></i>&nbsp;Github Repo</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero min-h-screen bg-base-200">
        <div class="hero-content text-center">
          <div class="max-w-md">
            <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold">Seamos amables unos con otros</h1>
            <br>
            <ul>
                <% todos.forEach( el => { %>
                    <li class='todoItem collection alert alert-warning shadow-lg' data-id='<%=el._id%>'>
                        <br>
                        <span class='<%= el.completed === true ? 'completed' : 'not'%>'><%= el.todo %></span>
                        <span class='del btn orange'> Borrar </span>
                    </li>
                <% }) %>    
            </ul>
            <br>
            <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold">Número de días cambiado para lo mejor: <%= left %></h1>
            <br>
            <form action="/todos/createTodo" method='POST'>
                <input class="textarea textarea-bordered" type="text" placeholder="Escribe tu mensaje." name='todoItem'>
                <input type="submit" class="btn">
            </form>
            <br>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>


    <div class="hero min-h-screen" style="background-image: url(/img/pc_station.jpg);">
        <div class="hero-overlay bg-opacity-60"></div>
        <div class="hero-content text-left text-neutral-content">
          <div class="max-w-md">
            <img src="/img/tls_logo_svg.svg" class="mb-5 text-5xl font-bold" id="acerca-de"/>
            <h1 class="mb-5 text-5xl font-bold">#SocialChallengeTLS</h1>
            <p class="mb-5">Este proyecto fue elaborado por estudiantes de Toulouse Lautrec, un instituto privado en el Perú que tiene como objetivo cultivar la creatividad y la innovación.</p>
            <p class="mb-5">Esperamos que disfrutes usando esta aplicación web tanto como nosotros disfrutamos creándola. Te queremos y siempre recuerdate de hablar good.</p>
            <button class="btn btn-primary"><a href="https://www.toulouselautrec.edu.pe/">Visita Toulouse</a></button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    <footer class="footer items-center p-4 bg-neutral text-neutral-content">
        <div class="items-center grid-flow-col">
          <p>Hecho con 	&hearts; por <a href="https://www.bryangranados.com/">Bryan Granados</a></p>
        </div> 
        <div class="grid-flow-col gap-4 md:place-self-center md:justify-self-end">
          <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/socialchallengeTLS"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="fill-current"><path d="M24 4.557c-.883.392-1.832.656-2.828.775 1.017-.609 1.798-1.574 2.165-2.724-.951.564-2.005.974-3.127 1.195-.897-.957-2.178-1.555-3.594-1.555-3.179 0-5.515 2.966-4.797 6.045-4.091-.205-7.719-2.165-10.148-5.144-1.29 2.213-.669 5.108 1.523 6.574-.806-.026-1.566-.247-2.229-.616-.054 2.281 1.581 4.415 3.949 4.89-.693.188-1.452.232-2.224.084.626 1.956 2.444 3.379 4.6 3.419-2.07 1.623-4.678 2.348-7.29 2.04 2.179 1.397 4.768 2.212 7.548 2.212 9.142 0 14.307-7.721 13.995-14.646.962-.695 1.797-1.562 2.457-2.549z"></path></svg>
          </a> 
          <a href="https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=toulouse+social+challenge"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="fill-current"><path d="M19.615 3.184c-3.604-.246-11.631-.245-15.23 0-3.897.266-4.356 2.62-4.385 8.816.029 6.185.484 8.549 4.385 8.816 3.6.245 11.626.246 15.23 0 3.897-.266 4.356-2.62 4.385-8.816-.029-6.185-.484-8.549-4.385-8.816zm-10.615 12.816v-8l8 3.993-8 4.007z"></path></svg></a>
        </div>
    </footer>
    <script src="js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
<html data-theme="coffee"></html>